william christopher ( born october 20 , 1932 ) is an american actor who is   best known for playing father john patrick francis mulcahy ( full character name ) , better known as father mulcahy , on the television series m*a*s*h , and private lester hummel on gomer pyle , u.s.m.c.   early life christopher attended new trier high school in winnetka , illinois , and graduated from wesleyan university in middletown , connecticut , with a b.a. in drama .

